Resolve ntp issues
------------------

There's a neat tool for ntp synchronisation.

Simply install this on client or server:
http://www.timesynctool.com/

Settings should be your favorite ntp server and an update time of 2 hours.
Afterwards you have to click on stop and start again to restart the service.

NetTime download link: http://www.timesynctool.com/NetTimeSetup-314.exe
